*** MUST BE IN INF-102/Week-8 DIRECTORY ***
COMPILE:
    mcs -out:twentyseven.exe twentyseven.cs
    javac twentyeight.java

    
RUN:
    mono twentyseven.exe "../pride-and-prejudice.txt"
    java twentyeight "../pride-and-prejudice.txt"


NOTE:
    The twentyeight.java program runs quickly, 
    but due to concurrency issues and multithreading,
    it may be necessary to quit program and re-run it (^C to quit) if
    the program hangs and solution is not immediate.
    
    

    